reviewText: This is great...original spooks which i hadn't seen! It was very enjoyable and worthy of being in a good collection.

Spooks is the British name for what is called MI-5 in the US.  You'll need a DVD player that transcends those idiotic local limitations, but there are more and more web-sites telling how to modify existing players. Spooks never fails to entertain. It's one of the best of the adventure series on the never-ending fight against terrorism, greed and selfishness.
